	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">北京龙泉寺开发了一个机器人，它还称不上有智慧</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-05-01 08:08:00 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">18</span>
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">53</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>

